The paper deals with cross-modal retrieval, which involves multiple modalities such as images, text, and audio. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision) is a likely sub-category as it deals with image and video processing. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a likely sub-category as it deals with retrieving relevant information from large datasets. cs.MM (Multimedia) is another likely sub-category as it deals with processing and analyzing multimedia data. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible sub-category as the paper proposes a machine learning-based approach. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is also a possible sub-category as the paper deals with text-based retrieval.
